    </td>
    <td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1" class="td">Yunes et al., 
     <xref rid="B40" ref-type="bibr" class="xref">1998a</xref>
    </td>
    <td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1" class="td">Bloom samples in the Patos Lagoon estuary at 2 sites.</td>
   </tr>
   <tr class="tr">
    <td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1" class="td">Oct-1995, Feb-1995 and Feb-1996</td>
    <td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1" class="td">Toxin in different growth stages</td>
    <td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1" class="td">
     <xref ref-type="table-fn" rid="TN3" class="xref">
      <sup class="sup">a</sup>
     </xref>0.01–0.19 μg.mg
     <sup class="sup">−1</sup> d.w.
    </td>
    <td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1" class="td">Yunes et al., 
